# Problem 3 – Print Unique Elements

### Code

```python
a = [10,20,30,20,40,10,50]

for i in a:
    if a.count(i) == 1:
        print(i)
```

### Output

```
30
40
50
```

### Logic

- Traverse the list.
- Print only those elements whose occurrence is exactly one.

